title: Josie Totah
itunes:title: Josie Totah
description:
Actress Josie Totah (SAVED BY THE BELL (reboot), GLEE, SPIDER-MAN: HOMECOMING) is on the pod reminiscing with Whitney about the pilot they shot together and talking about everything from paying someone to kidnap you to meeting Whoopi Goldberg.  Watch Josie in SAVED BY THE BELL streaming now on Peacock.
